Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.48,0:00:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,流下的淚水早已乾枯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.82,0:00:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,對血感到飢渴的孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡散發著\N{\fs8}\N{\r}天使柔和羽毛氣息飛舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗太陽不西沉的街道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.97,0:00:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,任誰都沉默不語
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,彷彿奇術般的運轉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.41,0:00:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,見不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.05,0:00:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡見不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,能夠拯救我們的神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,人們是疲憊的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,祭壇的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.67,0:01:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,機械夢想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Coppelia之柩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,從黑暗甦醒的光芒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,祭壇的羔羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,螺絲中斷的夢想究竟朝向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.90,0:01:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Noir
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,其乃自古命運之名
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,掌管死亡的兩名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,黑暗聖手誘使迷途者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,墜入業火深淵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:25.02,Title,,0,0,0,,#25 業火之淵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,儀式馬上就要準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.98,0:02:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你們成為真正NOlR\N{\fs8}\N{\r}的時刻終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,-是的\N{\fs8}\N{\r}-是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,為了讓你們兩人\N{\fs8}\N{\r}清淨身體、加強牽絆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.26,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,必須進行聖靈儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我仔細看看你們兩人的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.48,0:03:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,艾爾黛娜﹐我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,能得到妳的疼愛﹐我很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.43,0:03:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.66,0:03:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是啊﹐克洛維
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,真正的NOlR
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,受靈魂牽絆而結合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,誓言一同存活於黑暗的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.13,0:05:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,時候終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.27,0:06:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,被時間遺忘的這個場所
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,將改變今後的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.11,0:06:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,已經無人能阻擋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,霧香…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡不是妳該來的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.87,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.37,0:11:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,霧香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.61,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,儀式馬上就要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.98,0:12:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我不會讓任何人來妨礙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.02,0:12:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,這孩子的朋友也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優就拜託妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妳和米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.20,0:13:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今後一定會面對痛苦的試煉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,請妳一定要幫助那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.98,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,的確有時會因為愛而殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是﹐不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.68,0:13:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恨是絕對救不了人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恨…是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,憎恨是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,無法…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,救人…的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.06,0:14:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,這個地方在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.83,0:14:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是殉於黑暗的少女們\N{\fs8}\N{\r}較勁彼此的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,並選出真正NOlR的場所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.94,0:14:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,妳死在這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,也可說是…命運
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.79,0:14:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優．布克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.30,0:15:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,妳騙人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.21,0:16:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不要這樣﹐克洛維
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.64,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,求求妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看到在巴黎生活的妳和米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我感到非常…非常…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那明明應該是我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,明明應該是我才對！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,求求妳﹐克洛維
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不要再這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛維
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.75,0:17:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛維！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,NOlR…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛維是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.51,0:19:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,另一個我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.52,0:19:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我能夠殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.03,0:19:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,殺人之後﹐我會感到悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼…會變成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.29,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧﹐霧香
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,米雷優…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.28,0:21:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧﹐霧香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.62,0:22:34.32,ED,,0,0,0,,輕輕地被觸碰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:46.93,ED,,0,0,0,,終於察覺到臉頰的冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:52.81,ED,,0,0,0,,清晨醒來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.88,0:23:05.22,ED,,0,0,0,,突然開始注意到鳥鳴聲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.29,0:23:09.99,ED,,0,0,0,,什麼都還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.43,0:23:20.77,ED,,0,0,0,,不知內心追求的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.84,0:23:25.80,ED,,0,0,0,,總是望著天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:33.05,ED,,0,0,0,,不知何時開始這樣
